| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2156 — Recovery Inhibition (raworld)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0c44df5f-94e1-5c61-b1ac-068ad1f85da9"
